In order to save the Pan-Ancient Continent, the Dragon God has sealed his power in four dragon crystals. It is said that whoever obtains these four dragon crystals will gain the power of immortality and rule the entire Pan-Ancient Continent. 　　 Earth boy Long Xiang accidentally touched his grandfather's Dragon God bracelet, accidentally traveled through time and space, and came to Pan-Ancient Continent. He has a naughty personality and a funny manner, but he can distinguish between right and wrong at critical moments, jealous like hatred, and has a great sense of justice. This film highlights the intellectual elements, combines the spirit of chivalrous benevolence and bravery in Shiye culture and traditional culture, and makes Xiao Shiye a representative and symbol of wisdom and chivalry. At the same time, the material of this film is mostly taken from Shaoxing culture, which embodies typical Shaoxing characteristic elements such as awning boats, black felt hats, rice wine, Shenyuan, etc., and strives to fully display the regional characteristics and cultural features of Shaoxing.(translated from douban)

The protagonist Tianle who loves computer games and his baby dragon mysteriously went to the world of fighting dragons, and An Xiaoda, who was loyal to scientific research, learned that the world of fighting dragons controlled the destiny of mankind. And related to their mysteriously missing grandfather, An Xiaoda and Wang Meihan went to the world of fighting dragons with firm determination and strong curiosity. In order to save the world of fighting dragons, dragon fighters devoted themselves to destroying the black dead dragon forces. The battle for justice. An Xiaoda, Tianle, Wang Meihan, Ouyang(translated from douban)

The entire solar system, it is-Rakshasa Anwu. In order to defeat the Rakshasa•An Wu Yao Beast King, there is an ancient faction called "Dragon Wu Clan" that exists to train dragon fighters. The Longwu tribe is formed by six major star gates, namely, the Star Fire Gate which represents the fire image, the Hanshan Star Gate which represents the water image, the Lone Douxing Gate which represents the golden elephant, the Moon Sky Stars Gate which represents the light image, and The Molin Tianmen representing the wooden elephant and the Emperor Saxingmen representing the earth elephant. The members of the Longwu tribe are very mysterious, and they have always lived hidden in Liuyue Mountain, but no one has ever known why they existed and why they were hidden... Time flies, Raksha • Anwu will be resurrected again, and the Longwu tribe is selected The six sons of the family gathered together and shouldered the mission that they had since their birth. Then, in order to obtain the mecha beast dragon belonging to their own astrological power, the dragon fighting warriors came to the Beast Calling Mountain one after another. There, the six dragon fighting warriors had a perfect encounter with the mecha beast dragon, and successfully obtained the belonging My own mecha dragon... (translated from douban)

However, it was stubbornly resisted by the power of the earth. In the end, the Justice League represented by the vitality warriors defeated the Dark Legion after a bloody battle. The Dark Legion was driven back to the fantasy continent, and the vitality warrior sealed the evil leader in the mainland. The tower made him feel sorry for his mistakes, and mankind returned to a peaceful life. With each passing day and times changing, the evil leader gains new power and starts to wake up. The other party minions are doing evil everywhere to spread the dark energy in order to free the leader from imprisonment. From then on, everyone in the fantasy continent was in a state of panic. The patriarch of the cat clan who is responsible for guarding the forbidden area knows that if the dark negative energy cannot be stopped, the leader will get rid of the seal and become stronger, which will undoubtedly bring crisis and disaster to the entire universe again. The matter is of great importance and it is urgent. The patriarch sent his daughter, Mei Ya, to escape from the fantasy continent to the earth, so that she must find the descendants of the vitality warrior as soon as possible to stop the evil leader's conspiracy. At the same time, the leader's powerful minion high priest also knew that the matter was serious, and hurriedly sent his men to hunt down Maya in an attempt to sabotage and stop Maya's plan.(translated from douban)

title: Yuanqi Zhengjiu Dui
synopsis: In the face of major disasters, human beings often appear small and vulnerable. However, in the 21st century, with the rapid development of science and technology, artificial intelligence technology has been widely used. In the face of sudden natural and man-made disasters, human beings are no longer at a loss, and a vitality rescue team composed of humans and intelligent robots has emerged. When humans encounter natural and man-made disasters, whether it is natural disasters such as typhoons, earthquakes, avalanches, and floods, or large-scale accidents and other outdoor safety accidents, the vitality rescue team always rushes to the scene as soon as possible to quickly rescue. 　　 High-tech is also a double-edged sword. Dr. Lei, who loves peace, is very worried that rescue fighters are abused by some people, and even used at the military level, triggering a global arms race. So Dr. Lei boldly designed a hidden system—the emotional system was implanted into the electronic circuit of the rescue fighter. This emotional system must be the positive energy emotions of young people with pure and kind hearts in order to be activated and let rescue fighters exert their true power. If evil people want to use rescue warriors to do bad things, then rescue warriors can only exert one-tenth of their power, which is worse than the performance of ordinary production labor robots. 　　 This hidden system cannot be known to the outside world, lest criminals can crack it. In charge of all rescue operations, the chief of the rescue center issued an invitation letter to the youth of the whole society, hoping to cultivate a new group of rescue teams. Strictly selected by rescue fighters and rescue center computers, 12 boys and girls were finally selected to come to the rescue center to receive strict fire rescue training. Six of the boys honorably arranged to be partners of rescue fighters. They are mainly responsible for carrying out missions to the disaster site alongside rescue soldiers. The remaining six members served as support personnel, providing information and supplies on the transport ship. 　　 Just when everything went smoothly, an unknown bad guy was spotted. They hate rescue fighters and destroy them at all costs. Every time rescue soldiers conduct disaster relief activities, they will send terrible dinosaur soldiers to attack. At the disaster relief scene that is racing against time, you have to face the enemy's sneak attack, which is a severe test for rescue soldiers and small team members. In every battle and rescue mission, the team members will further understand their importance as a rescuer. They were also angry because of enemy attacks, and because of their anger, they only focused on fighting, forgetting the meaning of real rescue. However, the instructors in the rescue center were so tempted to let the children overcome their shortcomings time and time again, make continuous progress and maturity in thinking and rescue operations, and gradually become an excellent rescue team. 　　 The rescue fighters and rescue team members worked together and united to defeat every sabotage activity of the dinosaur fighters. The enemy was restless, and his true identity was finally revealed. It turned out to be a mad scientist who has always been jealous of Dr. Lei's talent. In order to prove that he is smarter than Dr. Lei, he did not hesitate to develop various robots to challenge rescue soldiers. In the end, he did not hesitate to sell the earth and join forces with terrible alien invaders to destroy the earth with terrible technology. Rescue soldiers and rescue team members will never compromise with them and do their best to protect all mankind. In the end, the mad scientist plan failed and was brought to justice, and the alien invaders fled in embarrassment and dared not come.(translated from douban)

title: Wu Long Xiaozi
synopsis: A long time ago, the ruler of the fantasy continent, the Great Demon King, in order to achieve the wolf ambition of ruling the entire universe, made waves, plundered resources and wreaked havoc everywhere. The righteous heroes stopped the devil with the power of friendship, justice and courage. The Great Demon King was sealed in an unknown place, hoping that he would regret his mistakes. However, the devil’s men are still destroying everywhere and trying to save the devil. The cat clan chief who is responsible for guarding the forbidden area of ​​the devil’s seal knows that if it is not stopped, the devil will get rid of the seal and become stronger. This will be good. The earth brings disaster. So the patriarch sent his daughter Mei Ya to look for three children who possessed the energy of friendship, justice, and courage to work together to prevent the destruction of the big devil. At the same time, Lei Long, the powerful minion of the Great Demon King, hurriedly sent his men to hunt down Mei Ya in an attempt to destroy Mei Ya's plan. In an action, Meiya got to know the young Xiangtian. Xiangtian is a righteous and awe-inspiring young man. By chance, Meiya discovered that Xiangtian was one of the teenagers who possessed righteous energy. After Xiangtian learned of his mission from Mei Ya, he resolutely agreed to help Mei Ya, determined to fight the big devil. Xiangtian found two other partners with friendship and courage, the honest and kind-hearted Aki and the cheerful and sunny Nana. Three wise and courageous children followed Meiya on a journey of justice.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Wu Long Xiao Zi Zhi Yong Chuang Le Huo Dao
synopsis: All the tea in the world lost the taste of tea overnight. In order to save the tea crisis, Oolong, Hainiu, and Ciwa bravely rushed to Lohas Island. (translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 乌龙小子之勇闯乐活岛

title: Mu Ling Baobei Zhi Chong Hui Fan Zhi Gu
synopsis: Lu Keke, the princess of Fanzhigu in the magical country, is tired of the life arranged by her father, always looking forward to going to the outside world. At this time, a few contaminated wood spirit treasures ran from Fanzhi Valley to the peaceful and beautiful riverside city, bringing destruction and disaster to the riverside city. Therefore, Princess Coco took the opportunity to pursue the wood spirit baby and came to the city of riverside. Zhang Disheng, a primary school student living in the riverside city, loves invention and exploration, and has always dreamed of becoming an explorer like his father. In a wonderful encounter, Zhang Disheng got to know Princess Coco and the two wooden spirit treasures Ula and Qilu she brought, and signed a wooden spirit contract with the wooden spirit treasure Qilu by accident, and possessed a magical nature. can. In order to restore the peace of their lives, purify the contaminated wood spirit treasures, and prevent them from destroying the environment and humans, Dison and Coco became good friends, overcoming numerous difficulties together, and embarking on their thrilling and interesting journey.(translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 木灵宝贝之重回帆智谷

title: Mu Qi Ling Zhi Lu Ying Zhan Ling
synopsis: The content of the plot mainly tells the complete animation of Mu Qiling's Green Shadow Fighting Spirit, a long-form original boutique series of cartoons with growth and fantasy as the themes and the traction of love as the theme. The Complete Works of Muqiling: Green Shadow Fighting Spirit tells the story of elementary school student Luo Fei who was brought to Green Shadow Island by the mysterious crystal in order to find his father. He met Muqiling Songka and Yali, and saved him to prove his ability to his father. Princess Lingxi and Xiaokui from the palace privately. Luo Fei learned from Lingxi that the evil Nether King was trying to resurrect and destroy the entire Green Shadow Island. Only by gathering five sealing crystals could he fight the Nether King, and the mysterious crystal that his father left Luo Fei was one of the five sealing crystals. One.(translated from douban)

title: Mu Qi Ling 2 Sheng Tian Ling Zhong
synopsis: Due to the destruction of water sources caused by human expansion, the ocean was eventually severely polluted. Because the giant algae Muqiling skyscraper in the ocean could not resist the erosion of marine pollution, it chose to use the dark power of pollution to carry out a retaliation plan. "The plants began to grow wildly on the human world and Luying Island, and the crisis broke out instantly. The primary school students Luo Fei, Haolei, and Ling Tianheng from the Riverside City returned to Green Shadow Island, and together with Princess Lingxi of Green Shadow Island and their contract Mu Qiling, they searched for a legendary holy heaven spirit seed with powerful purification ability. Chihua crisis. When Luo Fei and others successfully obtained the Holy Sky Spirit Seed after many tests, they not only had to fight against the troubles caused by the Skyscraper, but also faced the friction and misunderstandings between his companions, but Luo Fei did not shrink back and took his partners on the journey. In the journey of the deep sea capital, he finally succeeded in defeating the sky, purifying the chihua, and eliminating the crisis. (translated from douban)

title: Mu Qi Ling 3 Qi Ling Zhi Xin
synopsis: Muqiling Songka of the Giant Tree Clan dreamed of becoming the strongest warrior, so he went to the human world to find his contract partner Luo Fei to help him win the Warriors Championship. The magical spiritual power on Songka attracted the attention of the artificial intelligence "Gilga" who was eager to rule the world, and also made him stare at the source of energy of the strange spirit continent-"the heart of the strange spirit." If the heart of the strange spirit loses energy, the entire natural ecology will collapse. The God of Harmony, who guards the heart of strange spirits, turned the heart of strange spirits into five seeds, which were scattered and hidden among the five plant tribes. Gilga sent mechanical insect troops to search; Songka and Luo Fei were entrusted by the god of harmony and set foot on the collection. Seeds guard the journey of peace.(translated from douban)

title: UP Miao Zhiwu Kepu
synopsis: The story is introduced and explained one by one around the characteristics and functions of different plants and the cultural and historical origins of different plants together with the plant spirit Mu Qiling, sharing natural knowledge and historical and cultural learning interest with the audience.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Shui Man Jinshan
synopsis: "Shui Man Jin Shan" is a 52-episode domestic cartoon with the theme of "The Legend of the White Snake", one of the four major folk legends. Filmed by Nanjing Hongbao Film and Television Culture Company, Zhenjiang Radio, Film and Television Bureau and CCTV. CCTV animation director Chen Jiaqi will be the chief director of the show. Co-produced by Zhenjiang Media Group, Zhenjiang Water Conservancy Investment Company, Nanjing Hongbao Film and Television Culture Co., Ltd., and Central New Film Group, it will officially appear on the screen on March 13. The animation "Water Man Jinshan" is different from previous film and television works in that the film sets a negative character that is harmful to the world-the frog face water snake, which makes the storyline full of love and hate, and the conflict between justice and evil. Adapt to the viewing habits of young audiences. Another point of view is to use Xiaoqing as the main character in the story, describing that she never understood "love" to gradually understand what "love" is; from reckless impulse to resourcefulness and bravery, she created a realistic and educational significance. Animation works.(translated from douban)

title: Zhihui Zidan Che
synopsis: As soon as transfer student Yun Feng arrived at the new campus, he was hit by a toy car falling from the sky. Because of this "accident", Yunfeng got to know his neighbor Yanhui and also to the Smart Chariot. The smart chariot was invented by Professor Lang, who is obsessed with rail cars. The boss of the wealthy businessman Jin in Baidu Movie City has always wanted to steal for himself. With the help of Uncle Ma, Yunfeng demonstrated superb learning ability and won the game with his new friends Tianxiang and Yan Hui, without letting Boss Jin's strategy succeed.(translated from douban)

title: Shenqi A You
synopsis: The cartoon tells the story of a third grade elementary school student, Xiaomi, who has many worries and wishes. He made a wish to the starry sky alone, and was heard by the meteor-shaped universe man who happened to pass by. Ayo has the ability to instantly shuttle between various planets, which can help others realize different wishes. Xiaomi took Ayo back to her home as a partner. Since then, the life of a third-grade elementary school student, Xiaomi, has become no longer ordinary. Ayo uses his super powers to shuttle between the universe and continuously help Xiaomi realize various small wishes.(translated from douban)

title: Shenqi A You Zhi Zui Qiang Liuxing Ren
synopsis: The second complete episode of Ayo Magical tells the story in the last episode of the first season of Ayo Magical. In order to remove the paint for Xiaomi and travel to other planets, the robot meteors use Ayo’s kindness to escape, but it attracts a real Meteor Abba. A-you brought Abba the meteor man back to Xiaomi's house, but Xiaomi thought it was noisy, so Abba ran out. Abba finds it difficult to fulfill other people's wishes, is very sad, and wants to return to the universe. (translated from douban)

title: Xiao Ji Bu Hao Re
synopsis: In Happy Farm, there are three little chickens with different personalities, namely, Ding Ji, Xiaolong and Big Breast Chicken. Although rich in food and clothing, the lives of the chicks are not so peaceful. In the garbage dump outside the farm, there lived the tall and slender weasel brothers, the chubby weasel brothers. The two inherited the "historical chicken-eating mission" of the weasel family, but unfortunately, the weasel of his family except for an ancestor four generations ago The two brothers have never eaten chickens outside. In order to let this tragic fate end here, the two brothers study the methods of catching chickens at home every day, practice the skills of stealing chickens and dogs, harass the chickens whenever they have the opportunity, and monitor the farms through binoculars. Movement and quietness, looking for every gap in the defense of the chickens, always wanting to catch the chickens and eat them, always be defeated by the chickens, and finally stealing the chickens without losing the rice, leaving them with scars and dust.(translated from douban)

title: Xiao Ji Bu Hao Re Zhi Xian Dan Si
synopsis: Ji Xiaolong, a passionate young man who loves kung fu, grew up in the kung fu dream he knitted since he was a child, and dreamed of becoming a chicken hero one day. By chance, Ji Xiaolong entered the Salted Egg Temple and learned Kung Fu from the legendary "Kung Fu Master" Breasted Chicken, and became the guardian of the thousand-year-old salted egg. The elder brother King Kong who practiced martial arts with Xiaolong, he was mighty and impulsive, and always rushed to the forefront of everything. Little Junior Sister Tu Linglong is eloquent and quaint, inherited the agility of the assassin family, and can often strike the enemy unexpectedly. The informal chicken always teaches Ji Xiaolong some strange martial arts and makes many jokes. In the joy and laughter, the three apprentices smashed the salted egg conspiracy again and again by the Black Crow Gang, the biggest enemy of the Salted Egg Temple.(translated from douban)

title: Hua Jingling Zhi Xiha Da Maoxian
synopsis: This anime takes Sunflower Elf Xia Kui and Honeysuckle Elf Silver Bell as the protagonists. The two work together to find the sun fragments to solve the crisis of the Sun Kingdom as the main story line. The story takes place in the solar kingdom of the plant world. Because mushrooms like darkness and hate sunlight, they conspired to blow up the sun, but the plan did not succeed, but it blew a hole in the sun. The core and fragments of the sun were scattered all over the kingdom of the sun, and the sun’s damage was immediately caused. The kingdom is facing constant escalation and deterioration of various plant mutations, social chaos and other crises. In order to get rid of the troublesome mischief Xia Kui, the village chief took the opportunity to urge him and his small companion Yinling to go to the capital to find the queen to find a solution to the crisis. In the capital, the two won the savior selection contest in confusion, and were finally able to meet Chenxi, the queen of the sun kingdom. Then the two learned that they were descendants of the great heroes of the Kingdom Sunflower Elf and Honeysuckle Elf, and that the Sun Crisis incident was caused by the Mushroom Legion. From then on, the two had to shoulder the mission of saving the kingdom, and embarked on a hip-hop adventure to find the sun shards with the sun elf Puyoyo. During the journey, they encountered all kinds of weird events; mutant plant monsters and mushroom trio that often caused trouble. Of course, I have also made many new friends. They have grown and improved in the endless love, friendship and touch. In the end, they have gone through hardships to collect the sun fragments and successfully resolved the crisis in the sun kingdom. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Mo Dan Wang
synopsis: The King of Magic Ball tells that in 2030, junior high school student Ling Qili picked up a small flying saucer on the playground. This kind of flying saucer can enter the space of different dimensions to fight against the summoned beasts. Children who hold the flying saucer and manipulate the summoned beast to fight are called magic disk warriors. Ling Qili got acquainted with his magic disc "Fantasy Unicorn", and teamed up with a few friends to participate in the magic disc competition. As the competition progressed, a crisis in a different dimension gradually emerged. What is even more shocking is that this crisis was used by the opposing forces and the goal was directed at the earth. Ling Qili and his friends worked together, defying hardships and dangers, defeating one after another powerful opponents, saving the space of different dimensions, defending the earth, and finally becoming the true "magic disc war god"!(translated from douban)

title: Shen Ji Bao Meili
synopsis: Lao Jun made an invincible elixir, but he missed it and threw it down into the heavens, and fell into Luzhou (an ancient name of Hefei), was swallowed by an old hen, and transformed into a chicken with supernatural power. The old hen happened to meet the naughty boy, Baozi, and she became the alternative pet and all-around nanny of the Baozi family, named Baomei. In the process of life in the Baozi family, Meimei gradually has multiple identities-because of the elixir mana, it often becomes the savior of the Baozi family; because of the chicken-po's personality, it will become Baozi's nagging nanny for fear of avoiding it; because Chivalrous feelings, it has also become a mysterious comrade-in-arms of Baozi and his friends, to deal with all the injustices that they see in daily life together. In this way, Beauty, as an old hen, has gradually integrated into the human world and became the home of Baozi. Important family members. In the years of growing up with Baozi, it has slowly realized family affection, friendship and the true meaning of life.(translated from douban)

title: Shen Ji Bao Meili season2
synopsis: Lao Jun made an invincible elixir, but he missed it and threw it down into the heavens, and fell into Luzhou (an ancient name of Hefei), was swallowed by an old hen, and transformed into a chicken with supernatural power. The old hen happened to meet the naughty boy, Baozi, and she became the alternative pet and all-around nanny of the Baozi family, named Baomei. In the process of life at Baozi’s house, Meimei gradually acquired multiple identities...(translated from douban)

title: Ai Ke Mofa Shaonu
synopsis: The Magical Girl of Ai Ke is composed of three elements: music, magic, and beautiful girl. It mainly tells about 3 6th grade transfer students of Shinkai Academy. They are actually musical magical girls from the mysterious music world. They are secretly fighting against the evil noise demon. , Quietly maintaining the tranquility and peace of the world.(translated from douban)

title: Yu Qi Lin Zhi Xian Ling Qi Yu
synopsis: The anime tells the story of Xiaotian living in the fairyland. He has always dreamed of becoming a super fairy with spirit beasts just like the descendants of the fairy. One day, by chance, Xiaotian and the ancient spirit beast Yu Qilin met. The two became good friends, and they met to travel the rivers and lakes together to participate in the fairy contest. During the journey, they continued to fight and conquered all kinds of strange spirit beasts. They also met celestial spiritist partners such as Feng'er and Longma. Everyone worked hard for their respective goals, and Xiaotian and Yu Qilin also Gradually discovered his true mission.(translated from douban)

title: Zhandou Ba Ling Shou
synopsis: "Fight! "Spirit Beast" mainly tells about the young Guanghui and his friends Ai Li, Jin Feng and others, who were selected as the successors by the war spirit king. They need to learn and manipulate the power of gold, wood, water, fire, and earth, and the spirit of the five elements. The beasts fight together, against the evil spirit king! After many trials, Guanghui finally had the ultimate decisive battle with the Evil Spirit King. At the critical moment, Guanghui discovered that his best friend Moer had been possessed by the Evil Spirit King... (translated from douban)

title: Gang Jia Xiaolong Xia
synopsis: The Demon King, who was sealed by the God of Light for thousands of years, was resurrected and released a large number of demons lurking into the fairy tale world. In order to save all the fairy tale world, the God of Light dispatched zodiac warriors headed by Xiaolongxia to guard the peace of the fairy tale world. However, the super powers of the Chinese zodiac must rely on the power of the fairy tale savior to be fully utilized. Therefore, the guardian warriors headed by Xiaolongxia went to the human world to find the savior. The savior An Xiaodi, who was given a mission by the Chinese Zodiac, took the Chinese Zodiac to the fairy tales to seal demons and exorcise demons.(translated from douban)

title: Shouwang Zhengfeng
synopsis: When the world was still in chaos, there were five ancient giant brothers. They used their energy to build their own claws, and from the chaotic energy body, they pulled out the spirit beasts of their respective elements (fire spirit beast, water spirit beast) , Wood Spirit Beast, Golden Spirit Beast, Earth Spirit Beast). They control the spirit beasts to fight against each other, shaping the whole world during the game. But among the five giant gods, Vulcan Demon Yan has a different huge desire, he hopes to be the strongest and the only one. So he framed his comrades one after another, and absorbed all the power of their elemental beasts into his own claws. In the final battle with the earth god Panyao, Panyao rose up to resist, but still could not resist the demon. Yan has combined the attack of the ultimate spirit beast. She was about to fail, but Panyao, who still didn't give up at the end, used his brave sacrifice to discover a new magical power and perish with Mo Yan. Mo Yan failed, and countless little elves formed by the fragmentation of the ultimate spirit beast were scattered in every corner. The confrontation between justice and evil between the ancient giants, and the evil desires of Vulcan Demon Yan. In order to stop Mo Yan's attempt, Taiyu and his friends made clear their mission and shouldered this responsibility together, not only fighting for honor, but also fighting for peace. Let's set out GOGO team.(translated from douban)

title: Shouwang Zhengfeng Zhi Yuanshi Zhi Li
synopsis: The Beastmaster Battle Championship is the highest level event that only the team that wins the Beastmaster Battle Championship is eligible to participate in. A brand-new stage, brand-new rules, novel spirits, and an unknown mysterious power-the power of the original stone. The GOGO team that qualified in the qualifiers will challenge this brand new event and aspire to win the championship and become the strongest team worthy of the name. As the game progressed, the GOGO team, who knew nothing about the new rules and the new elves, gradually mastered the rules and improved their abilities. They became more and more courageous. They searched for mysterious rough stones and defeated one after another. A championship team. At the same time, there is a mask team among the teams participating in the competition. Their strength is extremely strong and their methods are brutal. They always give Tai Yu an uncomfortable and familiar feeling. When Tai Yu discovers that the mask team’s catastrophe is using a brand new collection of elves. When the dark power tried to rule the earth with the dark power, Tai Yu and the GOGO team decided to stop him at all costs. What's more surprising is that the true face of this tribulation turned out to be Ho Tian who fell into the magma. Not only that, he also took the remaining power of Demon Yan, ready to make a comeback again, let the chaotic power and darkness swallow the world. For honor and peace of the world, Tai Yu and the GOGO team once again shouldered the heavy responsibilities and stood in front of the chaotic giant Goten with unlimited power.(translated from douban)
